  <description><![CDATA[<p>The traditional Hotel Livigno is a homely hotel located within walking distance of the ski lifts. With cosy bedrooms, tasty food and a cosy wellness area with a sauna and steam room,  this hotel is a good choice for your next Italian ski break.</p>
<h2>Family run hotel</h2>
<p>Opened in 1912, the Hotel Livigno has lovingly run by the Mottini-Bormolini family for over 100 years. You can expect a warm welcome from the hotel staff, and a homely hotel stay with cosy rooms and tasty food. If you want to relax after a day on the slopes, we recommend the hotel's wellness area with sauna and steam room.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>The location of the hotel is ideal for a ski holiday. The Cassana lift is only 100 metres away and the local buses stop right outside the hotel so you can get to the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno">Livigno</a> easily. The hotel is 300 metres from the pedestrianised zone so you can walk there and browse shops along the way. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Livigno the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
