  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms</strong> are 18m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Mottolino Superior Rooms</strong> are 20m² and sleep two people. They have a balcony, tea &amp; coffee making facilities and a hydro massage bath with an overhead shower. These rooms are located on the 4th floor.</p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a whirlpool bath and a lounge. Suites are available on request, please call to book.  </p>
<p><strong>Twin Rooms for sole use</strong> are also available.</p>
<p>N.B: Superior Rooms and Suites are located on the 4th floor, which has ten steps from the 3rd floor where the lift stops.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
